{
  "stem": "7455.2",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 54,
      "text": "And the idea that the cellar is there gave him that we're going to be together.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 55,
      "text": "We're not going to go.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 56,
      "text": "But my aunts went back and brought us food.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 57,
      "text": "We were sitting in the garden.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 58,
      "text": "And then there were-- people were starting to go into the church, toward that side street-- processions and singing and praying.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 59,
      "text": "To them, it was a holiday.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 60,
      "text": "In meantime, my father, knowing that we have a place to, to sleep and to stay gave him courage.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 61,
      "text": "So they went.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 62,
      "text": "They said, we'll need some furniture, some beds, something, when we move into that cellar when it cools off.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 63,
      "text": "There were many bombed-out houses and burned down, so that there was raw material, wood.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 64,
      "text": "So he gathered wooden boards, dragged them, and they're going to make makeshift beds, makeshift table, like bunk beds.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 65,
      "text": "We didn't have nails, so with a rock, we found nails in some ruins.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 66,
      "text": "And then when my Aunt Rachel came, she went back to her house and got us a hammer and got nails, so he-- he was able to do it.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 67,
      "text": "And he started-- my brothers got busy.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 68,
      "text": "And when you are busy physically, it's helpful when you're broken up.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 69,
      "text": "So my father sort of gained back that energy, knowing that we have a place where to put-- lay our heads down.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 70,
      "text": "He made those beds, like bunk beds.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 71,
      "text": "They were not perfect, but they were-- now-- and boards across.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 72,
      "text": "And then they went to the outskirts of town to a farm and got straw, bunches of straw.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 73,
      "text": "And they got some prod-- products there.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 74,
      "text": "And we were waiting when it's cooled off to move in.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 75,
      "text": "And we moved into our cellar after three days sleeping in a garden.",
      "word_count": 13
    }
  ],
